                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3235" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0081</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9238 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1号店成长的烦恼：探寻自建物流之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New Challenges on Supply Chain Management for the NO.1 Store： Exploring Self-run Logistics</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李建斌，罗晓萌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1号店“网上超市”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链管理；B2C电子商务；自建物流；WMS系统优化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">supply chain management; B2C e-commerce; Self-run logistics; WMS optimization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1号店“网上超市”创立于2008年，被誉为“中国发展速度最快的综合类电子商务网站”。 1号店从建立之初就坚持自建物流体系，公司在快速发展中暴露出的一系列运营短板，让管理者体会到了成长的烦恼。面对“爆仓”，单纯地寻求扩大仓库库容并增加人力物力已经不能解决问题，如何从源头优化整个物流体系成了当务之急。本案例对1号店自建物流体系的运营现状进行了描述，并重点探讨了其中所遇到的瓶颈问题，梳理出优化思路。旨在深入剖析B2C电子商务企业存在的诸多供应链管理问题，以积极探索适应我国B2C电子商务企业特点的自建物流优化思路与实施对策。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The online supermarket “No. 1 Store” was established in 2008, and awarded as “China’s fastest growing comprehensive e-commerce website”. From the very beginning, the No.1 Store has no hesitation to build its own logistics network. However, managers of No. 1 Store suffer a lot of troubles during the company’s fast development, since a series of problems in relate to the supply chain operation have shown up. When “the capacity of the supply chain cannot afford the demand of order processing”, it is impossible to solve the problem simply through expanding the warehouse capacity and adding human resources and materials. The most urgent task is to optimize the operation of the whole supply chain from the source. Our case study aims to introduce the current situation of the company’s supply chain management, focus on figuring out the “bottleneck” of the supply chain operation, and propose the optimization ideas. In this way, we try to examine the supply chain problems facing Chinese B2C e-commerce companies in depth, and further explore the supply chain optimization ideas and implement strategies that can be applied to Chinese B2C e-commerce enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》、《供应链管理》、《物流管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业业务流程优化、供应链设计、仓储管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-07</td>
                            </tr>
